    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hi there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape! It\u2019s clean, handles beautifully on the road, and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve truly enjoyed driving it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to take the wheel and enjoy the journey. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
