      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Available is a 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo featuring the legendary 3.0L 2JZ-GTE inline-six engine. This powerplant utilizes a sequential twin-turbocharger configuration and a robust cast-iron block, delivering power through the highly coveted Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. The drivetrain is rounded out with a factory Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. This A80 chassis maintains its mechanical precision with a firm multi-link rear suspension and responsive hydraulic power steering. The forced induction system holds steady boost pressure, and the engine exhibits excellent thermal management. This is a mechanically sound, driver-quality example of Japanese over-engineering, perfect for the purist who prioritizes performance and drivetrain longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean title. Interior well-kept. Ready for immediate use.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This meticulously cared-for vehicle strikes the ideal balance between reliability and aesthetic appeal. The exterior presents beautifully in its original factory paint, showing only minor, superficial stone chips on the front fascia that are typical of responsible road use. All body panels are straight with consistent gaps, and the alloy wheels are free of significant curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a refined environment; the seats are supportive and free of tears, the carpets have been protected by floor mats since new, and every button, switch, and sensor operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts crisply, backed by a comprehensive service history that includes a recent fluid service and multi-point inspection. The tires offer plenty of life, and the brakes feel confident and firm. This is a solid, honest car that has been driven with care and is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_21_listing_5",
